some sort of heliocoil in there (if so what, how, where do I get it) or
3)Just deal with the 3 inch puddle of oil that collects under the car where
it is leaking around this stud.  All the other holes around the drain plate
are fine, so I can tighten it down ALMOST enough with these other nuts to
stop the oil leak, but not quite all the way.
